name: Nerd_Blue
description:
Kolaborasi Kunyahplastik dan Ikiwae:

Our upcycling plastic waste project that we did while in Mandalika, Lombok.For 5 days in a row we tried to collect a few trash scattered at Mandalika beach and tried to package it into an artwork that can be noteworthy and will remind us of the act of protecting the environment.
